sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Msiexec.EXE Initiated Network Connection Over HTTP
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description:
Detects an initiated network connection by "Msiexec.exe" over port 80 or 443.
Adversaries might abuse "msiexec.exe" to install and execute remotely hosted packages.

match_context.values: @{SourceIsIpv6=false; DestinationPort=80; Initiated=true; Protocol=tcp; SourceIp=192.168.2.16; DestinationPortName=http; EventID=3; DestinationIsIpv6=false; DestinationIp=45.95.11.217; DestinationHostname=vm2203315.stark-industries.solutions; SourcePort=49740; Image=C:\Windows\system32\msiexec.exe; SourceHostname=DESKTOP-B0T93D6.local}
